list.abstract: Normal（英[ˈnɔːml]，美[ˈnɔːrml]），英语单词。作形容词时，释义为正常的；标准的；常见的。作名词时，释义为正常状态；平均状态；典型。短语搭配为normal university（师范大学）。例句为“It's normal for countries to face tension.（国家面临紧张局势是正常的。）” 其反义词有abnormal、paranormal，形容词性近义词有standard、arm's-length，名词性近义词有criterion、level、prototype。
《Normal (Explicit)》是埃米纳姆演唱的一首歌曲，由Illadaproducer、S1、Lonestarrmuzik、Swish Allnet作曲，收录于埃米纳姆2018年8月31日发行的专辑《Kamikaze》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Is there any part of your body that's normal?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你身上有任何一个部位是正常的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Why aren't you small, like a normal potato? Because he is not a normal potato. He's got legs. Normal potatoes don't have legs. He's a super potato.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么不像那些正常的土豆那样小？因为它并不是一个正常的土豆，你看，他还有腿呢。正常的土豆是不会有腿的。他是一个超级土豆！

yingyinNormal.en: No, I would not characterize this as normal host behavior. Yet you're describing it as within normal parameters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我不会把这归为正常的接待员行为。但你将之描述成符合正常范围的。

yingyinNormal.en: This mirror looks normal to me. Daddy, where's your big tummy gone? What tummy?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我照这个镜子看起来挺正常的。爸爸，你的大肚子去哪了？什么肚子？

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, what are you guys looking at? Oh, just normal pictures of our regular family not having sex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们在看什么？ 哦,只是普通的照片正常的家庭却没有做爱。

yingyinNormal.en: When I was growing up, I didn't have a normal mom and dad or a regular family like everybody else.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我成长的过程中, 我不曾拥有真正的父爱和母爱，或者和别人一样拥有一个正常的家庭

yingyinNormal.en: So if you wanna be a normal kid, Auggie, then those are the rules. So let's go trick-or-treating. Okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 奥吉，如果你想当一个正常的孩子，这就是规则。所以我们去要糖果吧。好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And for 25 years I planned my revenge against the Federation. And forgot what it was like to live a normal life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我计划了25年，我都忘记该如何正常的生活了。

yingyinNormal.en: So Jack could be free. Now, this is the ultimate sacrifice and I understand that, but did you think about him having a normal childhood?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样杰克就自由了，这是最终极的牺牲，我很理解你，可你有没有想过让他过个正常的童年？

yingyinNormal.en: No one normal could have done that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 平常人可不会那样做。

yingyinNormal.en: The same way any normal person would.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跟任何正常人一样啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe we get through this program normal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许我们能像正常人一样完成实习。

yingyinNormal.en: Temperature, 82 degrees. PH balance, normal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 温度82华氏度，酸硷值正常。

yingyinNormal.en: You have no idea what I'd give to feel normal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不知道我愿意花多大代价变正常。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, because you know what I call that? Normal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，你知道我把这叫做什么吗？正常状态。

yingyinNormal.en: So? So they still seem normal. That's because they are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以呢？她们似乎很正常。

yingyinNormal.en: That was a weirdly specific answer. Well, everything is normal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 回答具体得很诡异啊。一切都很正常啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh! That's the kids pulling up right now. Just act normal. I was born normal. Not really. They said I came out with bangs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 孩子们刚停好车，表现正常一点。我生来就很正常，不对，他们说我出生时自带刘海。

yingyinNormal.en: No. No. But I'll go see a normal person movie with you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，但我可以陪你看一般人看的电影。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh-no, don't try and talk all normal with that thing in your ear.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别戴了耳环还装正常。
